name: Fiona

services.title: International Software Engineering Internship
services.description: Designed the frontend and developed the backend for an AI phone call system at a Tokyo startup using FastAPI and SQLAlchemy, contributing to a scalable solution that helps businesses capture missed revenue.

services.title: Leading AI-Human Interaction Research Presentation
services.description: Presented peer-reviewed research at the UCSC Psi Chi Symposium on how users react to AI speech errors and how responses can be tailored to influence emotions.

services.title: Cornell Tech - Break Through Tech AI Fellowship
services.description: Selected from approximately 3,600 applicants for a competitive year-long AI/ML fellowship with Cornell Tech, focusing on real-world applications of machine learning and AI fairness.

services.title: University Club Leadership & Workshop Development
services.description: Co-founded and lead as Internal Vice President of UC Santa Cruz Blueprint, a web and mobile app development club, where you design and host public workshops on industry tools and Agile methodologies.
